title: Tactical Carbine (Gunsite course)
description:
GUNSITE TACTICAL CARBINE I 
 
The combination of accuracy, firepower, and impressive terminal ballistics of the carbine makes it an extremely versatile tactical weapon. Now you can master its use with this comprehensive instructional video that covers all the critical skills of carbine use, including marksmanship, gunhandling, reloading, carry modes and tactical target engagement.
